>\n主要係消磨人既意志、熱情、信心<br />\n令人對同路人包容，同理心減低<br />\n用恥笑、嘲諷、批鬥、去脫離黃絲歸屬感 認同感，用內鬥令人對政治冷感<br />\n<br />\n係現今處境 呢種思想好有市場<br />\n我想提大家一句<br />\n記住初衷<br />\n記任大家講過<br />\n「輸就一齊輸」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:46:45.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\">以下係理論層面去解釋我上面嘅說話：（以下大部分內容皆摘錄自高學歷巴打post）</span><br />\n<br />\n1970年，蘇聯KGB特工Yuri Bezmenov叛變（無中譯，Google譯做 尤里&middot;貝茲諾夫），投靠美國，並公開蘇聯情報部門顛覆敵對國家社會嘅方法。由意志崩壞（demoralisation）開始，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>令到整個社會感到無助，唔團結，冷感，撕裂，以致崩潰，不戰而敗。</strong></span></span>呢套理論有學名，叫「顛覆」Subversion，而達到顛覆嘅行爲，就叫做 active measures / активные мероприятия。<br />\n<br />\n2019年，中華人民共和國依舊行使同一套理論，務求不需派兵嘅情況之下，摧毀香港。<br />\n<br />\nSubversion有四個步驟：demoralisation破壞意志+道德，destabilisation社會動盪，crisis災難點，normalisation正常化。<br />\n<br />\n以下係英文原版，RedDragon1會員詳盡中文譯本<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeVyEwJMdEQDTTxmeiJhXDLBPChrZSqCD7desS9xer9TZ?filename=mv5bmV1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmv5bmV1.png&h=e1116adf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcQpKGz3ABebBrQwoqsFrGwcYd25tgePiY4EEXPMVKUJ2?filename=yM38o9n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyM38o9n.png&h=00bad446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmW9VFcgYA4LW7oETL9vtvziBu4vcNxbZEb6qVwZaByEGr?filename=EvWRmV3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEvWRmV3.png&h=b10ab2c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qme14JkN3U92TbfNirSvwTA384oTRDoXrTEVHAQDSyY7nB?filename=CMfZvPo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCMfZvPo.png&h=32ead5cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個圖最後兩個顛覆步驟冇講清楚：<br />\n<br />\n「Crisis災難點」係指令到社會運作嘅機器失效，即係銀行停止發票，立法會停止會議，法院不能夠再審判。同時間，另類政府組織會冒起，如人民法院。<br />\n<br />\n「Crisis災難點」未直接入「Normalisation正常化」之前有可能會走兩條路：國際介入（多國戰爭），or內戰。但係如果冇呢兩樣嘢發生嘅話，就會直接入最後一步：<br />\n<br />\n「Normalisation正常化」，係指「社會動盪被入侵者完全制止」，蘇聯嘅例子係俄羅斯坦克車入城，將原本親蘇聯嘅內奸、政客殺哂（因爲已經冇利用價值），由外來嘅俄羅斯人清洗一切反抗聲音，「正常化」個動盪。<br />\n<br />\n希特拉亦曾經過類似嘅說話，進一步引證呢個理論<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQv4hujomsjtdjW5FHqUUDwcXoZUPDfrn6Fe1PTZs7LZL?filename=uNZ6dnn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuNZ6dnn.jpg&h=e3468b6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUrnf2dpzbx2WnkvULRzR3JF7GtsxkSGjEGkQiqj27PpA?filename=ykP9VBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FykP9VBU.jpg&h=ce499299&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a0b8169c986f69bc9556b872ce4a209bce1cc42","tid":2511085,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f687917f2699261c669c607e4dfed76e48209f56","tid":2511085,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:45:14.000Z","msg":"我信樓主, 佢係時事台首席智將, 幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:47:32.000Z","msg":"ching你有無ger級<br />\n點入行認真問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398064f676fea2da5975808d9ef2cb4f31d85f96","tid":2511085,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:48:26.000Z","msg":"老生常談<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊有人咁得閒日日上連登句句都係撩人鬧交，個心唔攰打咁多字都攰啦，除非係特登嘅"},{"pid":"9729063d6d8e67149e72cf8271fbe184de7db583","tid":2511085,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"946216b9f47d6e04f181b5a985fa1115083c172e","tid":2511085,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f687917f2699261c669c607e4dfed76e48209f56","tid":2511085,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:45:14.000Z","msg":"我信樓主, 佢係時事台首席智將, 幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:46:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.g